3.title: Welcome/Info Screen
3.content:
Phoneme Perception Test Instructions

Welcome to the phoneme perception test! Please read the following instructions carefully before starting the test.

Instructions:

Ensure you are in a quiet environment and, if possible, use headphones for better sound quality.

In each trial, you will be presented with a pair of Danish words. You will hear each word ONCE.

The words will play automatically and you will have to decide if they are the same or different words.

Repeat this process for each pair of words until the test is complete.

You will first be presented with three mock trials so that you can test the sound.

When you're ready, click the button below to start the test.
